title: The Killing Season - Radio Drama
description:
6 x 30 mins

This 6 part crime drama / thriller is credited to "Arthur Jefferson". In reality, it was written by the excellent R D Wingfield, however the BBC had decided it wanted no more of Wingfield's always excellent output, so he submitted this under a pen name!

The series is set in a small village at Christmas time. First one person is murdered then another, apparently without motive, until the truth becomes clear.......
